# Single quad face — exercises the quad → two-triangle triangulation path.
# Expected: 4 vertices, 4 UVs, 1 normal, 2 faces (triangulated as [0,1,2] and [0,2,3]).
v  0.0  0.0  0.0
v  1.0  0.0  0.0
v  1.0  1.0  0.0
v  0.0  1.0  0.0
vt 0.0  0.0
vt 1.0  0.0
vt 1.0  1.0
vt 0.0  1.0
vn 0.0  0.0  1.0
f  1/1/1 2/2/1 3/3/1 4/4/1
